02. @{bpen 2}  255,255,255  @{bpen 0}  - White
03. @{bpen 3} @{fg shine} 000,000,000  @{bpen 0} @{fg text} - Blue
12. @{bpen 12}  255,212,203  @{bpen 0}  - BrightRose
