@node 32c "The thirty colors project"

Set the screenmode to 32 colors or more.

To get the correct colors, lock the following pens :

16 . 192 112 000
20 . 242 131 122
21 . 128 000 048
22 . 224 172 064
23 . 100 100 100
24 . 144 112 080
25 . 207 150 060
26 . 220 220 220
27 . 068 068 068
28 . 064 160 192
29 . 000 112 064
30 . 062 132 177
31 . 048 192 112

Pens number 17, 18 & 19 must be kept unlocked cos' they're used by the pointer.

Why this ? Well, I noticed that the workbench lacked some colours despite being in 16 colors, and EaglePlayer's EMPYgui didn't looked so good. Now the 29-colors-patterns are quite pretty -> @{" [·] " system "SYS:Utilities/Multiview SCREEN 32colors/My32colzWB"}

That's it
@endnode

